OL,3,CCouple jailed after man run over by
OL,4,Ccar twice and robbed
OL,6,FA couple have both been jailed after a
OL,7,Fman was run over twice and then robbed
OL,8,Fwhile lying injured in the road.
OL,10,FMelvin Winters and Josie James met
OL,11,Ftheir victim in Wolverhampton on 2
OL,12,FJuly, 2025. There was an argument and
OL,13,Fthe victim, a 42-year-old man, walked
OL,14,Faway.
OL,16,FWinters, 46, hit him with the car,
OL,17,Fknocking him over. Winters then drove
OL,18,Fround and while the man was still on
OL,19,Fthe ground hit him with the car for a
OL,20,Fsecond time.
