OL,3,CCouple jailed after man run over by
OL,4,Ccar twice and robbed
OL,6,FJames, 32, then got out of the car and
OL,7,Ftook a gold chain from him before she
OL,8,Fand Winters drove off, leaving the man
OL,9,Fbadly injured on the road.
OL,11,FOfficers were called by ambulance
OL,12,Fcolleagues to the scene on Pope Road
OL,13,Fin The Scotlands at around 2.20pm. The
OL,14,Fman was treated by paramedics at the
OL,15,Fscene for serious injuries to his
OL,16,Flegs, ribs and shoulder.
OL,18,FWest Midlands Police says he is still
OL,19,Fcontinuing with his recovery.
