OL,3,CCouple jailed after man run over by
OL,4,Ccar twice and robbed
OL,6,FHe had been hit by a black Vauxhall
OL,7,FInsignia which was found abandoned in
OL,8,Fnearby Masefield Mews at around 3.05pm
OL,9,Fthe same day.
OL,11,FWinters and James, both from Bushbury,
OL,12,Fwere both arrested from separate
OL,13,Faddresses on 5 July, 2025.
OL,15,FWinters denied attempted murder and
OL,16,Frobbery. James also denied robbery.
OL,17,FHowever, following a trial at
OL,18,FWolverhampton Crown Court in December,
OL,19,Fthey were convicted of the charges.
