OL,3,CCouple jailed after man run over by
OL,4,Ccar twice and robbed
OL,6,FWinters was jailed for 24 years, with
OL,7,Fan additional four year extended
OL,8,Flicence on release.
OL,10,FJames was sentenced to nine years in
OL,11,Fprison.
OL,13,FDC Reece Markham, from the Major Crime
OL,14,FUnit, said: "Using a car as a weapon
OL,15,Fagainst another person is horrifyingly
OL,16,Fdangerous, and completely reckless -
OL,17,Fit could so easily have resulted in a
OL,18,Floss of life.
