OL,6,F"Then for the victim to be robbed
OL,7,Fwhilst helpless on the ground is
OL,8,Fshocking, and only compounded by the
OL,9,Ffact that the two offenders drove away
OL,10,Fleaving their victim to the mercy of
OL,11,Fhis significant injuries.
OL,13,F"Both refused to take responsibility
OL,14,Ffor their appalling actions but have
OL,15,Fnow rightly been convicted and jailed
OL,16,Ffor a considerable amount of time for
OL,17,Ftheir crime."
